fields.name: Daiwa Black Widow Lure Fishing Rod
fields.description: The Daiwa BW lure fishing rod is the ideal rod for Pike and Perch or even lure fishing for Wrass and Bass on shore.

fields.name: Abu Garcia Beast X Pike Spinning Rod
fields.description: The Abu Garcia Beast rod has been specifically designed for fishing medium to large pike with heavy lures!

fields.name: John Wilson Six Shooter Travel Spin Fishing Rod
fields.description: The John Wilson Six Shooter is perfect for life on the move whether camping, hiking, or as a reliable rod for the car, it's got you covered!

fields.name: Abu Garcia Venerate V2-C Spinning Rod
fields.description: The Abu Garcia Venerate V2-C Spinning Rod range have been designed as the perfect all-round spinning rods for lure fishing for predatory fish.

fields.name: Daiwa Ninja Spinning Reel
fields.description: The Daiwa Ninja spinning reel is the ideal choice for estuary fishing or river fishing!

fields.name: Abu Garcia Cardinal X Spinning Reel
fields.description: The Abu Garcia cardinal is a good affordable spinning reel suitable for all spinning needs.

fields.name: Okuma Solaris Reel
fields.description: The Okuma Solaris is a mid-range reel that packs a punch! Ideal for larger rivers or estuary fishing.

fields.name: Shimano Ultegra FC Fishing Reel
fields.description: The Shimano Ultegra spinning reel is a high-end reel that is capable of pretty much any spinning scenario.

fields.name: Fishing Bag
fields.description: The ideal fishing bag to store all your fishing equipment.

fields.name: Reclining Fishing Chair
fields.description: Ideal for long days at the lakes or beaches
